summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of the new Aquarium feature. All core functionality working correctly including aquarium view modal, empty state handling, filter/sort dropdowns, stats panel, and integration with existing menu system.
passed_tests: Main menu loads with all buttons including new AQUARIUM button
AQUARIUM button opens aquarium view modal successfully
Aquarium displays 'Your aquarium is empty!' message correctly
Filter dropdown contains all expected options (All Fish, Common+, Uncommon+, Rare+, Legendary)
Sort dropdown contains all expected options (Recent, Size, Rarity)
Stats panel displays Fish in Tank, Total Caught, Species, Rare Fish counts
Close button successfully dismisses aquarium modal
PLAY button loads stage select screen correctly
LEADERBOARD, BADGES, SETTINGS buttons open respective modals
Aquarium visual effects (bubbles, seaweed, coral, treasure chest) render correctly
Empty state UI displays appropriate message and styling
